# Skill: x-cli

## X-CLI Usage Guide

Comprehensive guide for using X-CLI effectively.

## Installation
```bash
brew tap dl-alexandre/homebrew-tap
brew install x
```

## Quick Commands

### Read Operations
```bash
x feed                    # Home timeline
x favorites               # Bookmarked tweets
x search "query"          # Search tweets
x user <handle>           # User profile
x tweet <id>              # Tweet detail
```

### Write Operations
```bash
x post "Hello"            # Create tweet
x like <id>               # Like tweet
x retweet <id>            # Retweet
x bookmark <id>           # Bookmark
```

## Native Transport (10x Faster)

1. Enable tracing:
```bash
export X_BROWSER_TRACE_TXID_FILE=/tmp/txids.jsonl
```

2. Harvest salt:
```bash
x like <tweet-id>
x harvest-txid /tmp/txids.jsonl
```

3. Configure:
```yaml
browser:
  static_salt: "your-58-char-salt"
```

4. Verify:
```bash
x doctor
```

